            . I also work at Mr. Baxter's. On the 8th of January, when I came in the morning, I missed my saw, and found it at Sims's.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18170416-164-person1259">
                  WILLIAM 
                  SIMS
               <interp inst="t18170416-164-person1259" type="surname" value="SIMS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170416-164-person1259" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170416-164-person1259" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a carpenter, and live in West-street. On the 14th of January, the prisoner asked me to buy three duplicates of tools; I gave him 4s. for them; He took me to the pawnbroker's, and I redeemed them; there were two saws and a plough-plane - They were claimed by Bolton and Jenkins. On the 25th of February, I met the prisoner in Field-lane, and secured him. I am sure he is the man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18170416-164-person1260">
                  JOHN 
                  SIMMONDS
               <interp inst="t18170416-164-person1260" type="surname" value="SIMMONDS"></interp>
