                     <interp inst="t18170416-164-person1260" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker. I remember the prisoner coming with Sims to redeem the saws and plane.</p>
               <p>HYAM BARNET. I took the prisoner into custody. He ran away - I secured him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18170416-164-person1261">
